{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"LocalFileSystemSync","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API_b98af8eade9a709904ec6e38c4e7c98a","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>File_and_Directory_Entries_API_b98af8eade9a709904ec6e38c4e7c98a</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_APIB\">文件系统 API</a>&nbsp;的&nbsp;<code>LocalFileSystemSync</code>&nbsp;接口允许你访问沙盒中的文件系统。它的目的是和 <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Worker\" title=\"en/DOM/Worker\">WebWorkers</a>&nbsp;一起使用。方法由 <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Worker\" title=\"En/DOM/Worker\">worker</a>&nbsp;对象实现。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关于这个文档","title":"关于这个文档","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个文档最后更新于 2012 年 3 月 2 日，并遵循&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/file-system-api/\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C 规范（工作草案）</a>，起草于 2011 年 4 月 19 日。</p>\n\n<p>这个规范或多或少已经废弃，没有得到大量的关注。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本概念","title":"基本概念","isH3":false,"content":"<p>通过在 WebWorker 中请求 <code>LocalFileSystemSync</code>&nbsp;对象，你可以请求访问沙盒文件系统。<code>window</code>&nbsp;对象的全局方法&nbsp;<code>requestFileSystemSync()</code>&nbsp;和 <code>resolveLocalFileSystemSyncURL()</code>&nbsp;暴露在 Worker 的全局域中。调用 <code>window.requestFileSystemSync()</code>&nbsp;来为你的 Web 应用创建新的存储器。</p>\n\n<p>更多概念请见&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/LocalFileSystem#basic_concepts\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/LocalFileSystem#Basic_concepts\">异步 API 的对应文章</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">//Taking care of the browser-specific prefix</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>requestFileSystemSync  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>requestFileSystemSync <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>webkitRequestFileSystemSync<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// The first parameter defines the type of storage: persistent or temporary</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Next, set the size of space needed (in bytes)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// initFs is the success callback</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// And the last one is the error callback</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// for denial of access and other errors.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> fs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">requestFileSystemSync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">TEMPORARY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1024</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token number\">1024</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/*1MB*/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>由于你使用了同步 API，你并不需要成功或者错误回调。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法概览","title":"方法概览","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>FileSystemSync <a href=\"#requestfilesystemsync\" title=\"#requestFileSystemSync\">requestFileSystemSync</a> (in unsigned short <em>type</em>, in long long <em>size</em>) raises <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\">FileException</a>; </code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>EntrySync <a href=\"#resolvelocalfilesystemsyncurl\" title=\"resolveLocalFileSystemSyncURL\">resolveLocalFileSystemSyncURL</a> (in DOMString <em>url</em>) raises <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\">FileException</a>;</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常量","title":"常量","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">常量</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">值</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a name=\"const_temporary\"><code>TEMPORARY</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>0</code></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>暂时的存储器，可由浏览器自主移除。</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a name=\"const_persistent\"><code>PERSISTENT</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n   <td>存在于浏览器的存储器，除非用户或者应用移除它。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"requestfilesystem","title":"requestFileSystemSync()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>请求一个文件系统，数据应该储存到这里。通过在 WebWorker 中使用这个全局方法（<code>window.requestFileSystemSync()</code>）请求 <code>LocalFileSystemSync</code>&nbsp;对象，来访问沙盒文件系统。&nbsp;[ RESEARCH ]</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>FileSystemSync</code> requestFileSystemSync(\n  in unsigned short type,\n  in unsigned long long size\n);</pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"参数\">参数</h5>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"type\">type</dt>\n <dd>文件系统的储存类型。值为&nbsp;<code><a href=\"#const_temporary\">TEMPORARY</a></code>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<code><a href=\"#const_persistent\">PERSISTENT</a>。</code></dd>\n <dt id=\"size\">size</dt>\n <dd>存储器的空间—按字节—你需要将其用于你的应用。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h5 id=\"返回值\">返回值</h5>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"filesystemsync\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileSystemSync\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileSystemSync\">FileSystemSync</a></code></dt>\n <dd>表示文件系统的对象。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h5 id=\"异常\">异常</h5>\n\n<p>这个方法可能产生&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\">FileException</a> ，带有下面的错误代码：</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">异常</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>SECURITY_ERROR</code></td>\n   <td>应用没有权限来访问文件系统接口。例如，你不能执行 <code>file://</code>&nbsp;。更多细节请见&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_APIs/Filesystem/Basic_Concepts_About_the_Filesystem_API#you_cannot_run_your_app_from_file:.2f.2f\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/DOM/File_APIs/Filesystem/Basic_Concepts_About_the_Filesystem_API#You_cannot_run_your_app_from_file:.2F.2F\">基本概念的文章</a>。</td>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resolvelocalfilesystemsyncurl","title":"resolveLocalFileSystemSyncURL()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>允许用户来检索文件或者目录的&nbsp;<code>Entry</code> ，由本地 URL 引用。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">void resolveLocalFileSystemURL(\n  in DOMString url\n);</pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"参数_2\">参数</h5>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"url\">url</dt>\n <dd>文件系统中的本地文件的 URL。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h5 id=\"返回值_2\">返回值</h5>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"entrysync\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/EntrySync\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/EntrySync\">EntrySync</a></code></dt>\n <dd>表示文件系统中条目的对象。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h5 id=\"异常_2\">异常</h5>\n\n<p>这个方法可能产生&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API/FileException\">FileException</a> ，带有下列错误代码：</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">异常</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ENCODING_ERR</code></td>\n   <td>URL 语法错误。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>NOT_FOUND_ERR</code></td>\n   <td>URL 结构正确，但是指向了不存在的资源。</td>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>SECURITY_ERR</code></td>\n   <td>应用没有权限来访问文件系统接口。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.LocalFileSystemSync","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<p>规范：<a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2009/dap/file-system/pub/FileSystem/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API: Directories and System Specification</a><span title=\"工作草案\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#e66e33;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">WD</span></p>\n\n<p>参考：<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\" title=\"en/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\">文件系统 API</a></p>\n\n<p>简介：&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/DOM/File_APIs/Filesystem/Basic_Concepts_About_the_Filesystem_API\" title=\"en/DOM/File_APIs/Filesystem/Basic_Concepts_About_the_Filesystem_API\">文件系统 API 的基本概念</a>。</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"关于这个文档","id":"关于这个文档"},{"text":"基本概念","id":"基本概念"},{"text":"方法概览","id":"方法概览"},{"text":"常量","id":"常量"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"文件系统 API 的 LocalFileSystemSync 接口允许你访问沙盒中的文件系统。它的目的是和 WebWorkers 一起使用。方法由 worker 对象实现。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"LocalFileSystemSync","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/file_and_directory_entries_api_b98af8eade9a709904ec6e38c4e7c98a","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/file_and_directory_entries_api_b98af8eade9a709904ec6e38c4e7c98a/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API_b98af8eade9a709904ec6e38c4e7c98a","title":"LocalFileSystemSync"}],"pageTitle":"LocalFileSystemSync | MDN","noIndexing":true}}